snippet.title: Fudgy Dice Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
From the fusion of dice games and deck builders rises a brand-new dice-builder. Embark on a crazy roguelike adventure with ramping relics and (literally) exploding dice or challenge your friends in local multiplayer with one of 7 unique characters. 

Wishlist Fudgy Dice on Steam now! 

Coming 2024
